1.title: Lillies for Lily

episode of.title: Home Grown Makeover with Frederique and Carter (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: Homeowners Ivan & Nicole are two weeks away from having their second child, a baby girl they'll name Lily. But before baby arrives, they desperately need more family-friendly living and dining rooms that fulfill their request for more storage and that bring the outdoors in. Frederique and Carter accomplish this with custom solutions such as a built-in banquette complete with an ivy-filled planter, a shoe rack created from the repurposing of an old shipping palette, a feature wall scattered with custom flower sconces filled with the unique roselily, and more.
